                <li>• Ownership transfers at end of term</li>
                <li>• Better for managing GST cash flow</li>
                <li>• Interest and depreciation deductible</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[#0d4d3e] mb-3">Chattel Mortgage</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 font-lato font-light">
                <li>• You own asset from day one</li>
                <li>• Full GST claimed upfront in one BAS</li>
                <li>• Lender holds security interest (mortgage)</li>
                <li>• Better for maximising immediate GST refund</li>
                <li>• Interest and depreciation deductible</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
