          <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">In practice, the total cost of each structure is very similar. The choice often comes down to GST cash flow preferences and accounting treatment. Your accountant can advise which is better for your specific situation. Nik Finance can arrange either structure from our panel of 130+ lenders.</p>
        </section>

